               <p>I <rs id="t17860531-66-viclabel344" type="occupation">keep an upholstery warehouse</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17860531-66-victim747 t17860531-66-viclabel344"></join> in <placeName id="t17860531-66-crimeloc345">Princes-street Lothbury</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17860531-66-crimeloc345" type="placeName" value="Princes-street Lothbury"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17860531-66-crimeloc345" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17860531-66-off342 t17860531-66-crimeloc345"></join>; on the 30th of May last, I lost some carpeting; this is mine; I can swear to it by this, and being folded up, and by the length of it: I did not miss it before Rigby the constable brought it in; I am sure I saw it on the Monday evening; I know it by the make and the colour.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17860531-66-person749">
                  RICHARD
                   PRITCHARD
               <interp inst="t17860531-66-person749" type="surname" value="PRITCHARD"></interp>
